data.description:
New remodel kitchen,New cover patio with privacy and nice backyard , you can park your car on the back door as well. The property located in really good neighborhood 12 minutes to airport , 10 minutes to medical center and like 15 minutes to downtown.

Renter will be responsible for water , electricity and maintain the backyard as well follow the HOA policy. No smoking inside the house, you can park up to 3 cars in front of the house and more cars in the backyard door also you can purchase an additional parking spot from HOA.
